{"tid":1026372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過年掃墓墳墓垮掉　壓中孝子孝孫1死3傷","createTime":"2019-02-18T05:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T11:23:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18d45012246449a616f2a599977b89ad2047a160","tid":1026372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:19:31.000Z","msg":"中國重慶的姚姓男子，過年期間帶著家人，去祭拜剛過世的岳父，沒想到拜到一半，才正要燒紙錢，才立好10多天的墓碑突然塌下，近千斤重的石塊壓中孝子孝孫，造成1死3傷。<br />\n《重慶晨報》周日（17日）報導，本月4日下午1時許，姚男帶著老婆、張姓女婿、孫子等一行4人，到才去世十多天的岳父墳前拜祭。姚男說，正當他們準備燒紙錢、放鞭炮的時候，他突聽到一聲「糟了」，還沒回頭，就有石塊把他擊倒，令他跌進墳邊的溝裡。回過神後一看，才蓋好十多天的墳墓，已連同墓碑、柱子、墳頭（墳墓隆起的部分）一起塌下，近千斤重的石塊接連滾落到地上，孫子的腳被壓住，放聲大哭；老婆的頭部被砸了一下、身上被石塊壓住；女婿身上也壓著石塊。後來，他拖著被壓傷的左腿，一邊爬到墳前，一邊打電話求救。<br />\n4人被送醫後，姚男的老婆因為傷勢過重，搶救無效死亡。女婿則是胸腔嚴重受傷，被轉送往其他醫院。而孫子右腳骨折、姚男左腳骨折。<br />\n知情人士透露，姚男的岳父於1月17日下葬，隔天姚家以5800元人民幣（約2.64萬元台幣）的價格，委託同村的村民立碑造墳，沒想到竟然是豆腐渣，才十多天就全部垮掉。<br />\n新聞曝光後，當地村委會、鎮政府已介入協調處理，當局認為，墳墓垮掉與地基有關。中國媒體指，中國人因為講究面子，近年農村地區有不少工匠會收費幫人立碑造墳，但施工工藝簡單，沒有標準規範，呼籲村民委託施工時，務必自行做好安全把關。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190218/640_a82430afc0d51d4a244f2461b58c9ca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190218%2F640_a82430afc0d51d4a244f2461b58c9ca6.jpg&h=eb95b911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190218/640_30ed2d4fb4b4a0f2e6e2a4a11a58f1d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190218%2F640_30ed2d4fb4b4a0f2e6e2a4a11a58f1d4.jpg&h=c0bf0026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190218/640_c2625a8524d70e48341c2717f518f43b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190218%2F640_c2625a8524d70e48341c2717f518f43b.jpg&h=49611f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190218/1519157/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190218%2F1519157%2F&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=c221e90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190218%2F1519157%2F&h=0cffdb13\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190218/1519157/</a>"},{"pid":"8e998799e51af47ad45126e81e55f0318c6e9ca3","tid":1026372,"uid":100347,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"又有支那新聞了<br />\n<br />\n連登仔好似城市論壇堆廢老又有精神食糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51e253f78872bd1a856575b841b8d3efe2c6346","tid":1026372,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"豆腐砸死人"},{"pid":"8b8472b1a6439fb092ae24cb8f1736013122852b","tid":1026372,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c61f2484a98a0bf6ba34777aca59da63e7b9e7a","tid":1026372,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/OXwS2Kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXwS2Kv.gif&h=00ca4037&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c42c7e09681986abdb89c37108cf86f15b5798c","tid":1026372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cac2785d3bfd542d33fd23d11c3dd0c1e01d331","tid":1026372,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c54f605b4a32608790b9c0828c1878cd4cd51521","tid":1026372,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201